title: Jesse Metcalfe
description:
Jesse Metcalfe returns with stories about his acting start in soaps, his love of “Basketball Diaries,” his role on “Desperate Housewives,” his great hair, and his new movie with Bruce Willis called, “Fortress.” Plus, Lala reveals the big acting tip she picked up from Jesse!
